title: Dreft | Amazinghood: Kelly Rowland’s Journey Begins
description:
Stay tuned as Dreft takes you through the stages of Kelly Rowland and her son Titan’s Journey of Amazinghood. Dreft Stage 1: Newborn Detergent is hypoallergenic and the #1 choice of pediatricians. It’s specially formulated to be gentle on baby’s skin and to give every baby’s clothes a gentle clean with every wash. So, it’s the only brand Kelly trusts to take care of Titan’s clothes.

With Dreft Laundry Detergent’s new family of products for every stage of babyhood, you’re covered every step of the way along the big, messy, beautiful Journey of Amazinghood.
